{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/leetcode-3-explanation/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"1-문제-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"1 문제 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 문제 확인</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/longest-substring-without-repeating-characters/description/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters</a>\n<br>\n주어진 문자열에서 <strong>중복되는 문자가 없는</strong> 가장 긴 부분 문자열을 찾는 문제입니다. <strong>substring</strong>, 즉 주어진 문자열에서 끊김이 없는 문자열을 찾는 것이 포인트입니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-코드\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C\" aria-label=\"2 코드 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 코드</h2>\n<p><strong>코드 1</strong><br>\n처리시간 146ms</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">lengthOfLongestSubstring</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        max_len <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> left <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> right <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> right <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            left_c<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> right_c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> s<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>left<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>right<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> right_c <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>right_c<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> left<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                left <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>right_c<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\n            <span class=\"token builtin\">dict</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>right_c<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> right\n            max_len <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>max_len<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> right<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>left<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            right <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> max_len</code></pre></div>\n<p><br>\n<strong>코드 2</strong> (개선)<br>\n처리시간 122ms</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">lengthOfLongestSubstring</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">str</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        used <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        max_length <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> start <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> index<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> char <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">enumerate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> char <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> used <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> start <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> used<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>char<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                start <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> used<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>char<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                max_length <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>max_length<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> index <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> start <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n            used<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>char<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> index\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> max_length</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"3-피드백\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%ED%94%BC%EB%93%9C%EB%B0%B1\" aria-label=\"3 피드백 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 피드백</h2>\n<p>이번 문제는 풀면서 책의 힌트(<strong>투 포인터</strong> 활용)를 살짝 봤습니다 😭. 그래서 <strong>코드 1</strong>과 <strong>코드 2</strong>의 핵심 아이디어는 동일합니다. 세부적으로 조금의 차이는 있지만, 처리시간을 포함해 대부분이 비슷합니다.<br>\n<br>\n주요 아이디어는 다음과 같습니다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>슬라이딩 윈도우를 위한 투 포인터 <code class=\"language-text\">left</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">right</code>를 준비한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">right</code>를 한 칸씩 늘려가며 최대 길이를 갱신한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">right</code>에 해당하는 문자는 항상 딕셔너리에 저장, 갱신한다.</li>\n<li>만약 <code class=\"language-text\">right</code> 문자가 이미 존재한다면 중복이므로, 이전 인덱스+1 로 <code class=\"language-text\">left</code>를 갱신한다.</li>\n<li>이때, 인덱스+1 의 값이 <code class=\"language-text\">left</code>보다 작으면 안 된다. (되돌아가는 과정에서 중복 발생 가능)</li>\n</ol>\n<p><br>\n<strong>코드 2</strong>에서는 <code class=\"language-text\">for</code> 문을 통해 <code class=\"language-text\">right</code> 대신 <code class=\"language-text\">char</code>를,  <code class=\"language-text\">left</code> 대신 <code class=\"language-text\">start</code>를 사용합니다.<br>\n<br>\n위의 아이디어를 이용하면, 중복 없이 슬라이딩 윈도우를 유지하며 최댓값 갱신이 가능합니다. 예를 들어 <code class=\"language-text\">cabcd</code>의 경우, 다음과 같은 과정을 거칩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\">left<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'c'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'c'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\nleft<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'c'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\nleft<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'c'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'b'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span>\nleft<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'c'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span>\nleft<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>3번째 <code class=\"language-text\">c</code>에서 0번째 <code class=\"language-text\">c</code>를 확인한 순간 <code class=\"language-text\">left</code>가 <code class=\"language-text\">a</code>로 넘어가는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.<br>\n<br>\n위의 아이디어 설명중 5번은 다음과 같은 예시 때문에 존재합니다.<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">abccccbd</code><br>\n6번째 <code class=\"language-text\">b</code>를 <code class=\"language-text\">right</code>로 탐색할 때, 딕셔너리 중 기존 0번째 <code class=\"language-text\">b</code>가 존재합니다. 이때 0번째 <code class=\"language-text\">b</code> 다음인 <code class=\"language-text\">c</code>를 바로 불러오게 되면 그사이에 <code class=\"language-text\">cccc</code>로 인해 제외시켰던 중복이 다시 생기게 됩니다. 따라서 <code class=\"language-text\">dict[right_c] >= left</code> 같은 조건이 필요합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-요약정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"4 요약정리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 요약정리</h2>\n<p><strong>슬라이딩 윈도우</strong>와 <strong>투 포인터</strong>를 활용하자.<br>\n딕셔너리를 통해 <strong>O(1)</strong> 로 문자 사용 여부에 접근하자.</p>\n<h2 id=\"source\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#source\" aria-label=\"source permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Source</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>『파이썬 알고리즘 인터뷰』 <em>-박상길 지음</em><br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/onlybooks/algorithm-interview\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/onlybooks/algorithm-interview</a></li>\n<li>leetcode<br>\n<a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/longest-substring-without-repeating-characters/description/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://leetcode.com/problems/longest-substring-without-repeating-characters/description/</a></li>\n</ul>","id":"573a708b-20cd-5174-b550-db6594e5ed1e","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\">1. 문제 확인</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C\">2. 코드</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-%ED%94%BC%EB%93%9C%EB%B0%B1\">3. 피드백</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#4-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\">4. 요약정리</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#source\">Source</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Leetcode 3번 풀이","summary":"Leetcode 3번 중복 없는 가장 긴 문자열 문제 풀이, 투포인터","date":"2022.12.12.","categories":["Algorithm","Leetcode"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/bd5b96dad01a641177884d7f75cd6831/08